@startuml
title SD-EMR-01 환자 검색 / 목록
' UC Trace: UC2-1-1, UC2-1-2

actor Doctor as d
participant "CDSS UI" as ui
participant "Django CDSS\nEMR Proxy (UC2)" as emr
participant "OpenEMR API" as openemr

group 환자 검색
  d -> ui : 이름/ID 입력
  ui -> emr : GET /patients?query=...
  emr -> openemr : REST /patients/search
  openemr --> emr : patient list
  emr -> emr : cache upsert
  emr --> ui : patient list DTO
end group

group 환자 목록 표시
  ui --> d : 환자 목록 화면 렌더링
end group
@enduml
